Usage: assemble_proto_model [-help] [-cpf_file <cpfFileName>]
                            [-mmmc_file <mmmcfileName>] {-blockdir {blockDesignDir [protoModeldirName]}} {-topdir {topDesignDir [protoModelDirName]}}

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-blockdir {blockDesignDir [protoModeldirName]}
                              # The directory which contains the block level
                              # design (string, optional)
-cpf_file <cpfFileName>       # Chip level cpf file (string, optional)
-mmmc_file <mmmcfileName>     # Chip level mmmc file (string, optional)
-topdir {topDesignDir [protoModelDirName]}
                              # The directory which contains the top level
                              # design (string, optional)